## Routing

| Route | Description |
|---|---|
| `/` | Product landing page (placeholder — needs building) |
| `/login` | Email + password login |
| `/signup` | Registration with email confirmation via Supabase authentication |
| `/admin` | Dashboard |
| `/admin/[section]` | Each content section editor |
| `/admin/sections` | Section visibility + drag-to-reorder manager |
| `/admin/theme` | Full theme customizer with live preview |
| `/admin/resume` | Resume builder — 3 templates, PDF preview, download |
| `/admin/inbox` | Contact form submissions inbox |
| `/portfolio/[uid]` | Public portfolio (single-scroll, all visible sections) |
| `/portfolio/[uid]/resume` | Public resume viewer with download |
| `/api/contact/[uid]` | POST — stores contact form submission |

