## Environment variables in use

```
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=        ← publishable key (new Supabase format)
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=            ← secret key (new Supabase format)
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=                  ← Vercel deployment URL
PUPPETEER_EXECUTABLE_PATH=            ← only needed locally, not used in prod
```

